WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:03.073
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:03.074 --> 00:00:11.536
I have some things I want to talk to you about, but first of all, I just want to say thank you for all the likes, the subscribes, and the comments.

00:00:11.537 --> 00:00:20.384
It's a true blessing to us, and we just want to say thank you for supporting this YouTube channel as you have. God bless you all.

00:00:20.385 --> 00:00:32.649
I pray for you daily that the Lord increases you in every area of your life—physically, spiritually, financially, emotionally, everything—that the Lord will give you abundant overflow in your homes.

00:00:32.650 --> 00:00:44.370
I just want to say thank you from the bottom of our hearts for supporting this YouTube channel, and I appreciate your prayers for my family. I appreciate all your prayers.

00:00:44.371 --> 00:00:53.600
I'm going to do a video that I've already done before, but I felt because of the time that's passed since I made the video that I could do it better.

00:00:53.601 --> 00:01:01.287
I listened back to it and I thought, 'I think I can do better at that.'So, let's give it a shot.

00:01:01.288 --> 00:01:12.356
I've told you before how the Lord took me out of my body and I shot up into outer space.

00:01:12.357 --> 00:01:27.374
I could see the Lord, though from His midway up, I could not see anything during the whole visitation.

00:01:27.375 --> 00:01:39.502
I don't know if it was God the Father or Jesus, but I'm going to tell you, we were in outer space and I could see the planets.

00:01:39.503 --> 00:01:50.022
It was like everything was shrunk down. I know they're millions of miles apart, but everything in the solar system seemed so small to us.

00:01:50.023 --> 00:02:02.202
We were looking at it like the planets were right there. I could see Saturn, Jupiter, and Mars.

00:02:02.203 --> 00:02:14.062
I could see it all, but we were standing right next to the Sun the whole time. The Sun was massive, and it was over to my right.

00:02:14.063 --> 00:02:21.623
The Lord was also to the right, and I was looking out at the Sun when He spoke to me.

00:02:21.624 --> 00:02:31.155
He said, 'Brandon, how long does it take for the Sun's light to get to the Earth?'I knew the answer.

00:02:31.156 --> 00:02:43.957
I said, 'It takes like eight minutes and 20 some seconds.'Right then, I knew the answer, but now I've probably butchered it.

00:02:43.958 --> 00:03:01.272
I told the Lord that at 186,000 miles per second, the light travels from the Sun and takes 8 minutes and 27 seconds to get to the Earth.

00:03:01.273 --> 00:03:39.781
He asked me, 'Brandon, what is faster than the speed of light?'I said, 'I don't know, Lord.'He said, 'The speed of thought.'He said, 'Brandon, whenever you die and you come to be with Me, you will travel at the speed of thought, not at the speed of light.'The speed of thought is actually way faster than the speed of light because you are there instantly instead of traveling at 186,000 miles per second.

00:03:39.782 --> 00:03:54.958
He was telling me all this, and then He talked to me about how far the nearest star is, which is light-years away.

00:03:54.959 --> 00:04:10.603
I don't remember exactly how far it was, but He told me it would take thousands of years to get there even at 186,000 miles per second.

00:04:10.604 --> 00:04:21.134
Then He said, 'I want to take you and show you something.'All of a sudden, we were instantaneously there.

00:04:21.135 --> 00:04:36.220
This is where it gets good. What I could see before me when we went into this room was a massive white room.

00:04:36.221 --> 00:04:57.448
There was no beginning and no end to this room. The light in the room was so piercing, but there was no ceiling, no floor, nothing.

00:04:57.449 --> 00:05:08.510
It was like a dimension in itself. There before me was the universe.

00:05:08.511 --> 00:05:18.195
This is heavy, but I'm telling you all it's fact. The universe was in its own dimension.

00:05:18.196 --> 00:05:34.694
He created a room for the universe; all the galaxies were inside of another dimension that was endless.

00:05:34.695 --> 00:05:44.895
Before me, the universe was moving at the speed of light, being created.

00:05:44.896 --> 00:06:06.527
I could see inside of this massive area; it looked like cauliflower clouds—like thunderclouds moving very slowly—but it was forming right in front of my face.

00:06:06.528 --> 00:06:26.502
Stars were forming inside of this dimension, shrunk down. Though moving at 186,000 miles per second, it looked slow because He controls time.

00:06:26.503 --> 00:06:46.457
He is in control of all time; time does not exist around Him. At 186,000 miles per second, creating right before my eyes, it was moving so slowly.

00:06:46.458 --> 00:06:58.909
I could see how big it was since the beginning when He spoke it into existence, 'Let there be light.'All the things He said in Genesis were moving.

00:06:58.910 --> 00:07:09.995
It was the size of a Volkswagen Beetle—I don't know why, but that's the way it stood out to me.

00:07:09.996 --> 00:07:28.764
It was that shape and it was moving in all directions—downward, upward, left, right, north, south, east, west—all at the same time, creating from the center.

00:07:28.765 --> 00:07:50.048
It was like a thunderstorm, moving slowly like thunderclouds, all being formed and created inside of this room.

00:07:50.049 --> 00:08:11.116
Stars were moving and being created from every direction. It was all moving equally.

00:08:11.117 --> 00:08:33.782
He spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, you know in My Word where it says I can measure the span of the universe in My hand?'He said, 'I'm going to show you how I do it.'He took that universe and shrunk it down right before my eyes.

00:08:33.783 --> 00:08:42.841
He said, 'I create and I am able to manipulate it.'It was like clay before Him.

00:08:42.842 --> 00:09:11.319
He said, 'Brandon, it is in a dimension in itself,'and He could stretch it out or shrink it.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:51.855
He put it in His hand, and He had the whole universe—billions and billions of galaxies—shrunk down in this dimension.

00:09:51.856 --> 00:10:12.546
He said, 'Look, I can step into it.'He stretched it out and said, 'I can step into it or I can shrink it down, but Brandon, I measure it all in My hand.'He put it in His hand—it was stretched out and he showed it to me like a cube—and it was still growing.

00:10:12.547 --> 00:10:26.775
It never stopped; stars were still forming in His hand as He was holding it.

00:10:26.776 --> 00:10:55.677
No matter how He stretched it or shrank it, it was still being created.

00:10:55.678 --> 00:11:06.032
I just stood there and watched. I know I wasn't in my body; this was more than just a dream.

00:11:06.033 --> 00:11:10.735
This happened to me over 20 years ago and I've never forgotten it.

00:11:10.736 --> 00:11:28.964
I remember every detail like it was yesterday, other than the numbers. I've told you I've overcome my learning disabilities.

00:11:28.965 --> 00:11:40.279
He took me then and said, 'I want to show you something else,'and He showed me Heaven.

00:11:40.280 --> 00:11:50.267
Heaven was a massive planet, about the size of three Jupiters.

00:11:50.268 --> 00:12:02.418
Heaven is a massive planet, like a dimension in itself. I could see the gold; it was pure light.

00:12:02.419 --> 00:12:14.620
It was beyond comprehension; I cannot give it adequate justice with words.

00:12:14.621 --> 00:12:30.319
It was inside its own dimension. The universe was on the edge of Heaven.

00:12:30.320 --> 00:12:35.999
We were standing out there again, and I was looking at all the walls.

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:48.448
There are massive walls all around Heaven, and I could see buildings—all kinds of houses and buildings.

00:12:48.449 --> 00:13:05.533
It's like a major city, but beautiful beyond words. I could see the walls formed with gold and all kinds of beautiful stones.

00:13:05.534 --> 00:13:40.606
Then all of a sudden I looked up, and the sky above me was filled with beautiful pinks, purples, and whites, swirled like a paisley print.

00:13:40.607 --> 00:13:52.686
He said, 'Brandon, this is My portion; I set this aside for Myself, Heaven. But son, I'm giving you the universe.

00:13:52.687 --> 00:14:06.878
All the galaxies are going to be yours.'He said that is the portion He is giving to His kids, the born-again believers.

00:14:06.879 --> 00:14:47.415
When you come home to be with Me after the thousand-year reign, you will spend eternity traveling at the speed of thought throughout all the galaxies and universes, going from one to another.

00:14:47.416 --> 00:15:00.237
There are planets and stars being made, and you will rule and reign forever and ever with Me over eternity in those places.

00:15:00.238 --> 00:15:03.622
Why people say, 'Why would I want my own galaxy?'I don't know.

00:15:03.623 --> 00:15:11.674
We have a mansion in Heaven, but I'm trying to tell you what I saw.

00:15:11.675 --> 00:15:26.294
Then He said to me, 'Do you see all that?'And I could see the stars being formed before me.

00:15:26.295 --> 00:15:32.437
That dimension was still being spread out, but He had opened it up and we were inside of it now.

00:15:32.438 --> 00:15:43.767
Heaven was on the edge of it, and the universe and all the galaxies were on this side.

00:15:43.768 --> 00:15:50.255
He told me, 'You will rule and reign with Me forever and ever.'You're never going to get bored.

00:15:50.256 --> 00:16:00.327
You'll travel at the speed of thought to all your brothers and sisters; the whole body of Christ is going to be ruling and reigning.

00:16:00.328 --> 00:16:13.064
He's creating a new Heaven and a new Earth. Folks, we have an amazing future.

00:16:13.065 --> 00:16:22.242
God has an amazing plan for His church and His people. It is not for us to be down and out.

00:16:22.243 --> 00:16:46.222
We're going to rule and reign with Him for all eternity. The Lord told me, 'Brandon, I am a big, big God.

00:16:46.223 --> 00:16:55.143
I want you to go back and tell My people they think way too small.

00:16:55.144 --> 00:17:16.258
I want them to start believing Me for bigger, for I am a big God able to do exceedingly abundantly above all they dare ask or think.'Remember that.

00:17:16.259 --> 00:17:31.079
He has it all in His hand. There are more stars than there are grains of sand on our beaches.

00:17:31.080 --> 00:17:38.648
You'll never be able to wrap your mind around how big the universe is.

00:17:38.649 --> 00:17:55.879
It's basically endless, but He's able to control it. It's still being created because life is still being created.

00:17:55.880 --> 00:18:07.042
People are getting born again every single day, and He has a place assigned just for you.

00:18:07.043 --> 00:18:15.624
One day, when we rule and reign with Him, whatever that purpose is, I have no idea.

00:18:15.625 --> 00:18:32.885
All I know is there's a big plan for us, and He loves you. I know that when we get there, He'll have a galaxy for you.

00:18:32.886 --> 00:18:42.056
The Milky Way is the galaxy we're in, but there are billions more.

00:18:42.057 --> 00:18:54.447
I hope I didn't butcher that, but I tried my best to explain something so amazing and life-changing.

00:18:54.448 --> 00:19:00.832
He wanted me to tell you how big He really is and that He's endless.

00:19:00.833 --> 00:19:08.610
Nothing is too hard for Him. All things are possible to him who believes. You just have to believe with simple faith.

00:19:08.611 --> 00:19:23.005
If you have the faith of a mustard seed, He said you would move a mountain.

00:19:23.006 --> 00:19:28.622
If you do not doubt in your heart, you'll have whatsoever things you say—Mark 11:24.

00:19:28.623 --> 00:19:48.552
I'm believing with all my heart for big things in 2024 and 2025. It's time to believe God for the impossible today.

00:19:48.553 --> 00:19:57.631
He's no respecter of persons, and what God did for one, He'll do for another. God loves you and He has an amazing plan.

00:19:57.632 --> 00:20:02.119
Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:20:02.120 --> 00:20:09.678
Think about that. He wants you to be in health; He wants you to be above and not beneath.

00:20:09.679 --> 00:20:13.415
He wants you to have a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:20:13.416 --> 00:20:28.472
We are the salt of the earth, ministering to our neighbors and telling them that Jesus loves them and is coming soon.

00:20:28.473 --> 00:20:39.834
Jesus is coming soon, folks. I hope you're ready. I hope your heart is prepared.

00:20:39.835 --> 00:20:43.574
A lot of people say, 'I don't believe in the Rapture.'That's your problem.

00:20:43.575 --> 00:21:02.945
I do, and He's coming back for you and me and those who believe and are seeking Him daily. Let me pray for you.

00:21:02.946 --> 00:21:18.058
Father, I thank You for 'big.'I thank You, God, for 'huge.'I thank You for 'ginormous'—that You are an awesome God able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we'd ask or think.

00:21:18.059 --> 00:21:26.635
I thank You, God, that You're creating something amazing for me, my children, my wife, and all my friends and family.

00:21:26.636 --> 00:21:49.749
You have eternity; time is endless with You. You have everything in the span of Your hand.

00:21:49.750 --> 00:22:05.319
Father, I thank You that You come and visit me, that You have a plan for my life, and that You love me enough to show me secret things and things to come—for us to believe You for bigger, not smaller.

00:22:05.320 --> 00:22:11.254
We get out of our stinking thinking, poverty, and lack. Father, You're a God of more than enough.

00:22:11.255 --> 00:22:20.284
I've seen the edges of Heaven; there's no poverty in Heaven.

00:22:20.285 --> 00:22:36.751
There's only abundance, overflow of gold, rubies, sapphires, diamonds, pearls, and beautiful gemstones beyond comprehension.

00:22:36.752 --> 00:22:46.798
I thank You, Father, that You've created this for us and that You love us enough not to give us some shack down by the river, but to give us a mansion.

00:22:46.799 --> 00:22:55.830
You said You'd give us our heart's desires, God, and I thank You for that.

00:22:55.831 --> 00:23:16.678
You said, 'Beloved, I wish there would be on earth as it is in heaven.'I thank You, Father, that we don't have to struggle on this earth; we can have more than enough.

00:23:16.679 --> 00:23:30.757
Lord, we give You glory, honor, and praise. We call every single person watching this video healed, whole, and well, delivered from oppression.

00:23:30.758 --> 00:23:37.240
Strongholds are broken off their lives, set free by the blood of the Lamb and the word of their testimony.

00:23:37.241 --> 00:24:05.390
We thank You, Lord, that marriages are restored, homes are good, and children are blessed. Father, I thank You for a great year in 2024.

00:24:05.391 --> 00:24:16.203
By the time we get to the end of 2024, we will say, 'Look what the Lord has done.'Great is Your faithfulness to me.

00:24:16.204 --> 00:24:42.282
All my life You have been faithful and so, so good. Thank You, Father.

00:24:42.283 --> 00:25:11.316
I will sing and give You praise for Your goodness today. Thank You that we're healed and whole.

00:25:11.317 --> 00:25:21.514
I bless You, Lord. I just want to say thank you all for watching and supporting us.

00:25:21.514 --> 00:25:30.435
I hope this video blessed you and inspires you to believe for bigger.

00:25:30.436 --> 00:25:52.708
Jesus loves you so much and has great plans ahead for you. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:25:52.709 --> 00:26:04.720
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you. We will see you next time. Have a blessed day. Bye-bye.

